Subject: [PATCH 04/16] qom: Fix memory leak in object_property_set_link()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

RH-Author: Amos Kong <akong@redhat.com>
